not announced in advance, those bastards) means that Vox will be up tonight or shortly after the servers come back up. H/Cok will take her on tonight, unless the server comes up later than 5 pm PST. If they skip BEFORE 8 pm PST, we HAVE to take her down tonight, Jan. 31st. Otherwise if they try and fail, we will be up for her on Thursday, Feb. 1st. I will be alerting the email list of this eventuality, but also wanted to warn you here. Get your cold resist gear ready.<br>
<br>
The raid will be for all classes, levels 40+ EXCEPT Wizards, Mages and Necromancers. Those classes must be 45+. All cold and magic resists should be a minumum of 70 WITHOUT buffs, the higher the better. Those with the Fearless or resist disciplines, I suggest using one of those disciplines as the fight commences. <br>
<br>
Those who wish to go on this raid should also bring with them 30pp (this is a little lower than I would like but should recoup some of the costs) which we will distribute to the clerics, enchanters and other classes who need reagents for their buffs (such as symbols, runes, etc.). This money will be collected and passed out to those of this class who attend BEFORE the raid begins. Those classes are ESSENTIAL to the success of the raid, and they often have to shell out MAJOR bucks just to buff folks on large scale raids. This is one way to say &quot;Thank you for your buffs&quot; and to interest them in coming. I will post the loot policy on this thread as well.<br>
